Class DAGNetwork

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.core.delta.NNLayer<DAGNetwork>
      • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.net.DAGNetwork
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DAGNode, Serializable

    public class DAGNetwork
extends NNLayer<DAGNetwork>
implements DAGNode
    Builds a network NNLayer components, assumed to form a directed acyclic graph with a single output. Supplied builder methods designed to build linear sequence of units acting on the current output node.
    Author:
    Andrew Charneski
